{"tid":683030,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"6月尾東京七日六夜行程求指點","createTime":"2018-05-29T10:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T16:21:10.000Z","uid":18677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6987237650190461f08538fcf7642a4290baf3c","tid":683030,"uid":18677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"細佬第一次去東京 會同女友2個去 希望有去開既巴打可以指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住宿: AIRBNB (廣尾站附近）<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 25/6（星期一）<br />\n<br />\n早上0750就會到NRT 預係機場搞下地鐵卷 wifi蛋個啲 跟住會坐book左既SKYLINER出上野 跟手去上野公園/阿美橫町 三四點左右就去BNB check in 整理下行李就去涉谷行加晚餐<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n<br />\n原宿＞新宿＞池袋 （都係去啲大路景點，想知再講）<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n<br />\n淺草＞SKYTREE＞東京站＞芝公園＞東京鐵塔睇夜景<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n<br />\n築地＞銀座＞台場＞秋葉原<br />\n<br />\nDay 5，6<br />\n<br />\n箱根，鐮倉，江之島，橫濱（未firm點分配，希望巴打們指點下，特別係可以買咩pass會抵玩啲，e.g. JR廣域，江之島pass）<br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n<br />\n晏就三點幾機，所以應該冇時間去啲乜<br />\n<br />\n求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77512be342bf30bc33e0d8d47656c629a2fb1ea9","tid":683030,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3e37ee7f7aa7bdd329e0287cd5c57ca8ff9068d","tid":683030,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fed389cb2b3d7736684be3feffc9416d51f87a","tid":683030,"uid":18677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77512be342bf30bc33e0d8d47656c629a2fb1ea9","tid":683030,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"so